{"tid":2517997,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[哥倫比亞示威] 哥倫比亞對示威民眾動武 國際社會譴責","createTime":"2021-05-05T17:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T19:08:26.000Z","uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"90ffb75a5b33a61906ded4540f1ca35c7baf8003","tid":2517997,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2021-05-05/1024/20210505004135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2021-05-05%2F1024%2F20210505004135.jpg&h=b2a18cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">數以萬計的哥倫比亞人4月28日開始走上街頭抗議，一開始是反對政府新提出的稅制改革，後來更演變成是對總統杜克（Ivan Duque）政府的示威。(圖／路透社)</span><br />\n<br />\n聯合國形容，在哥倫比亞持續數日的反政府示威中，釀成多人喪命的悲劇，是該國維安人員「過度使用武力」的結果，此事今天也遭國際社會責難。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，官方資料顯示，哥倫比亞民眾在與維安部隊的衝突中，共有19人喪命、846人受傷。在這樣的悲劇發生後，聯合國（UN）、美國、歐洲聯盟（EU）、人權組織同聲批評此事。<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞的人權監察組織，一個獨立於政府之外的國家機構，稱有89人列為「失蹤」。<br />\n<br />\n數以萬計的哥倫比亞人4月28日開始走上街頭抗議，一開始是反對政府新提出的稅制改革，後來更演變成是對總統杜克（Ivan Duque）政府的示威。<br />\n<br />\n抗議民眾今天在全國幾個地方堵住道路，同時也在哥倫比亞首都波哥大（Bogota）和該國西部的卡利（Cali）展開新的示威抗議。<br />\n<br />\n卡利是哥倫比亞的第3大城市，也是受到這波動盪影響最嚴重的地方。4月30日起，當地便出現軍人獲令上街巡邏的情況。<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞國防部在全國各地部署4萬7500名軍警，而光是在卡利就有700名軍人、500名鎮暴警察，並派有1800名其他類型的警察和兩架直升機在當地。<br />\n<br />\n針對一起昨晚發生在卡利，警方對示威民眾「開火」，據報造成多人傷亡的事件，聯合國人權事務高級專員公署（Office of the UN High Commissioner for Human Rights, OHCHR）今天表示「極為震驚」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210505002878-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20210505002878-260408&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=389fe0a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210505002878-260408</a>"},{"pid":"25b12e4eaebba37730778a17188885cec2a7a655","tid":2517997,"uid":89182,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:22:37.000Z","msg":"UN：震驚你班撚屌夠膽搞事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緬甸人香港人唔好望，你都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cbd3f09195a18709dbae703fd39f12c03453fb","tid":2517997,"uid":58120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:24:18.000Z","msg":"我都係早幾分鐘上9gag先見到有post號召聲援<br />\n呢單野完全無新聞咁濟, 痴撚線"},{"pid":"2820a6ef59e21be3c7734ca5bc764b1355b6dcfb","tid":2517997,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:24:19.000Z","msg":"驚完早啲訓"},{"pid":"db804d33f4a696900b2ca56d21448f5ac86c4cb4","tid":2517997,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a5df59585de84ae8988b6a9760cbc56254771c","tid":2517997,"uid":257216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"好似冇乜主流媒體報道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd330bf533d99f891f14d846a1a9438e467a7a50","tid":2517997,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><em><span class=\"red\">譴責</span></em></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27294ff070737daba09056fdd6c290aa42be9fcb","tid":2517997,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:37:46.000Z","msg":"無限譴責"},{"pid":"80cd61c1cb0f273f162da1fe39629033185a0e3f","tid":2517997,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:38:18.000Z","msg":"各國警暴裡面 香港算唔算嚴重<br />\n西班牙警察係癲到搵車撞鳩d加泰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51